00:33:22,130 --> 00:33:24,413
Which means it would still
pose a serious threat, no?

784
00:33:24,437 --> 00:33:26,241
But if we give the
medications a chance,

785
00:33:26,265 --> 00:33:28,069
then maybe we can
bypass the need

