because of my recommendation.

853
00:36:58,781 --> 00:37:02,220
Hold on, are you... are
you blaming yourself?

854
00:37:04,439 --> 00:37:05,982
Before you spiral
out any further,

855
00:37:06,006 --> 00:37:09,246
